            "answer_text": "Bisexual is just a word in order to help others understand your sexuality. There is no set official requirements that much be reached in order to obtain the unimportant title of bisexual. For me it just means you like girls and guys. There are countless definitions for differnet sexuality. Some of my friends identify themselves as sluts even though it is normally derogatory. Basically don't worry about if other people will think of what you call yourself just consider yourself whatever you want. Another example is that I say my eye color is layered because that's what it looks like to me. However a lot of people claim that it's hazel but then I'll say hazel is all the colors mixed together but guess what it is only a word to discribe my own ideas. So whatever you decide to call yourself no one has any right to say otherwise because your sexuality is up to you and not them. ",
